            <thetext>Steps to reproduce:

1. Select a value.
2. Close the popup (if it isn&#39;t closed automatically)
3. Select another value.
4. Close the popup (if it isn&#39;t closed automatically)
5. Open popup with Alt + Down Arrow key
6. Preselect another value (select a value but don&#39;t close the popup)
7. Cancel the selection by pressing Escape.

Instead of showing the 2nd value, the one we last selected it, the 1st one is shown.

This was introduced by fixing #4538.</thetext>
